          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COINC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The deuterons were detected by the upper",
                " arm of the detecting system, whereas the g-quanta",
                " from the PI0 meson decay were detected by the",
                " lower arm of the system."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MWPC",
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The upper (deuteron) arm of the detecting",
                " system consists of drift chambers and three",
                " layers of plastic scintillators having thickness of",
                " 2, 12, and 20 cm, respectively."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The lower (g-quanta) arm of the detecting",
                " system consists of a calorimeter that consisted of",
                " NaI and  CsI scintillators. The size of the CsI",
                " crystals was 60x60x150 mm, whereas the size of NaI",
                " crystals was 55x115x300 mm."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Total measurement error is given for each",
                " experimental point and takes into account the",
                " statistical and systematic uncertainties."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-1",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The systematic uncertainty takes into account",
                " the measurement uncertainty of the target tensor",
                " polarization (3.5%)."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-2",
                "minimum_value": 5.0,
                "maximum_value": 7.0,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " During the identification of the channel",
                " for the gd -> dpi0 reaction, it was impossible to",
                " remove the background, which was estimated to range",
                " from 5% to 7% depending on the photon energy."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-3",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": 5.0,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The error induced by the neglect of the",
                " contribution of longitudinal virtual photons to the",
                " reaction amplitude at small electron scattering",
                " angles, does not exceed 5%."
              ]
            }
          ],
